<title>UK: Bombril to raise coupons on two dlr bonds.</title>
<headline>Bombril to raise coupons on two dlr bonds.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bombril SA is set to increase the coupons on two of its dollar bonds after an extraordinary bondholder meeting, Credit Agricole Indosuez said on Friday as lead manager of the deals.</p>
<p>The meeting was required after Bombril acquired an 80 percent stake in Italian food company Cirio Spa.</p>
<p>The issues, $93 million of Series A notes due 1998 and $57 million of Series B notes due 1998 which both now carry an 8.00 percent coupon, will pay 9.25 percent when the purchase is completed, Credit Agricole Indosuez said.</p>
<p>-- Dan Lalor, London newsroom +44 171 542 8863</p>
